Bearings Inc said it filed with theSecurities and Exchange Commission a registration statementcovering a 40 mln dlr issue of convertible subordinateddebentures due 2012.    Proceeds will be used to fund substantially fund theredemption on October 26 of the company's 8-1/2 pct convertiblesubordinated debentures of 2012. Bearings will buy back theconvertible debt at 105.95 pct of 1,000 dlr face amount, plusaccrued interest.    The company said it named Merrill Lynch Capital Markets asunderwriter of the offering. Reuter&#3;